<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>Title</title>
	<style>
		.bList{
			padding: 0;
			margin: 0;
			list-style-type: none;
		}
		.bList>li{
			float: left;
			width: 10%;
			height: 40px;
			line-height: 40px;
			border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(128, 128, 128);
			overflow: hidden;
			text-overflow: ellipsis;
		}
		.bList>li:nth-child(5n+2){
			width: 60%;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<h1>게시판 목록</h1>
	<div><a href="/write">글쓰기</a></div>
	<div>총 레코드 수 : <%=totalRecord%>, 현재페이지 :<%=pageNum%></div>
	<ul class="bList">
		<li>번호</li>
		<li>제목</li>
		<li>글쓴이</li>
		<li>조회수</li>
		<li>등록일</li>
		<% for(var idx = 0; idx<records.length; idx++){ %>
			<li><%=records[idx].no%></li>
			<li><a href="/view?no=<%=records[idx].no%>"><%=records[idx].subject%></a></li>
			<li><%=records[idx].username%></li>
			<li><%=records[idx].hit%></li>
			<li><%=records[idx].writedate%></li>

		<% } %>
	</ul>
	<div>
		수정
		삭제
	</div>
</body>
</html>